    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Impatiens glauca var. ecalcarata: A.; B––Flower side view; C.; D––Flower frontal view; E––Lower sepal; F––Lateral united petals; G––Dorsal petal; H.––Stamen; I––Capsule; J––Seed; K––Leaf dorsal view." ;
